A man was caught on video beating an elderly truck driver along the side of Route 95 near Baltimore, Maryland  . 
  Tommy Solis was driving by and filmed the incident and tried to break up the fight . 
  The man punched, kicked and threw the old man after he hit the aggressor's car and cut him off . 
  The aggressor refused to stop and got in the face of Solis and his friend . 
  The old man was left passed out cold on the road . 
 